I've had this app for quite a while, but while trying to use it at my jobsite today, it wouldn't open. Apparently I need a data connection to use an app that I've paid for? I'd recommend fixing that for the next customer.
replyContent: Google's licensing services requires an occasional internet connection for the license check. After this occurs the license is valid for weeks at a time without any internet connection. Please let us know if you have any additional questions by emailing us at techsupport@cyberprodigy.com

content: Overall pretty solid. Ive used this conduit app almost daily now and find it quicker and better than other apps i have used.
Do not let select the size of conduit
replyContent: This app uses the generic cosecant method to determine bend lengths. The hand bender you use will account for the EMT size differences. 90 degree bend deduct lengths do account for EMT size, 1/2" through 4" conduit sizes can be set in the preferences tab. Please let us know if you have any additional questions. Email: techsupport@cyberprodigy.com

replyContent: The additional calculation you are looking for was added in version 1.4.4 of Conduit Bender Elite.   The overall offset (offset and roll) is shown with an orange arrow on both rolling offset calculators and the value is displayed in orange text.  Please let us know if you have any additional questions or concerns.
